short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Developed a program to conveniently manage bookmarks

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
To make the bookmark bar easier to manage and use effectively, I developed a bookmark search and pin feature.
This feature is designed to ensure that bookmarks are added under relevant categories in the bookmark bar, making the bookmark system and toolbar more practical and convenient.
As a result, it enables more efficient use of the bookmarking functionality.
